{"tid":1853900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大：布口罩未確認防病毒","createTime":"2020-01-31T08:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T15:16:38.000Z","uid":35774,"like":362,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"882b354065109d13505a2ec0ae964ca71e47b02a","tid":1853900,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/poly9999999/5992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpoly9999999%2F5992&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=aa555585\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/poly9999999/5992</a><br />\n<br />\n【理大口罩未確認防病毒】<br />\n<br />\n有報導指香港理工大學(理大)研發了一款新的「布口罩」，可以防菌及可作多次清洗重用，並已獲得國際認証，預計最快10多日後能供應巿場。<br />\n<br />\n理大學生會向理大查詢時，理大特此澄清，理大是受香港紡織及成衣研發中心(HKRITA)委託研發防菌物料，該物料主要是防細菌及霉菌，暫未有數據驗證該物料可有效防病毒。理大就相關物料的產品開發只用於家居產品，例如床單，並沒有涉及防病毒類型之口罩。"},{"pid":"50cfeb05c16779c1cf758136322546987aae79af","tid":1853900,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"609a9762339454b7d0f25e0f1dba85f1725cbd92","tid":1853900,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f9834cb7a260638716086f72ea5b32890516fa43","tid":1853900,"uid":124983,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"中國賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c118c005d17540565c19ced94e704d501fa482","tid":1853900,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"pish 1/10"},{"pid":"f687eaebaa4e010ac432da13d3ae2a3843561567","tid":1853900,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"pish 2/10"},{"pid":"130dd9250bde0f14bf18469c4f9488193399a5c1","tid":1853900,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:40:10.000Z","msg":"pish 3/10"},{"pid":"e5a701d25dfe22963c8593cf74da917